<section class="page-letters">
  <div class="page-letters__inner">

    <!-- ── Hero ── -->
    <header class="page-letters__hero">
      <p class="page-letters__eyebrow">Free &middot; five letters &middot; five days</p>

      <h1 class="page-letters__title">
        Five letters to find your way<br>back to your <em>self</em>.
      </h1>

      <p class="page-letters__subtitle">
        The inside story of getting lost in a life that looked right —
        and the small weekly practice that brought me back.
        For everyone who feels the question underneath: <em>is this it?</em>
      </p>

      <a href="#letters-form" class="page-letters__cta-btn">Send me the first letter &rarr;</a>
      <p class="page-letters__cta-note">Free. The first letter arrives within the hour.<br>Reply to any of them — I read every one.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- ── § i — Recognition ── -->
    <div class="page-letters__section">
      <p class="page-letters__marker">&sect; i</p>
      <h2 class="page-letters__heading">You function. You perform.<br>On paper, things are fine.</h2>

      <ul class="page-letters__mirror">
        <li>You smile when expected and work past exhaustion.</li>
        <li>Every achievement feels strangely hollow once you reach it.</li>
        <li>You scroll to quiet the question, not to answer it.</li>
        <li>You've read the books and heard the podcasts — other people's answers.</li>
        <li>Somewhere along the way, your own voice grew quiet.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="page-letters__body-em">If you recognized yourself in three of these, the letters were written for you.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ── § ii — The letters ── -->
    <div class="page-letters__section">
      <p class="page-letters__marker">&sect; ii</p>
      <h2 class="page-letters__heading">What arrives in your inbox</h2>

      <p class="page-letters__body">
        Five short letters over five days. Not a course. Not a funnel.
        One honest story and one practice in each — things you can try the same day, alone, with pen and paper.
      </p>

      <ol class="page-letters__list">
        <li>
          <span class="page-letters__list-num">Letter I</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-title">Lost — the life that looks right and feels wrong</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-sub">Naming the autopilot. Why "fine" is the most dangerous word you use.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="page-letters__list-num">Letter II</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-title">The voice you stopped hearing</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-sub">How to begin listening to your self again — and why journaling works when thinking doesn't.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="page-letters__list-num">Letter III</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-title">Feelings are weather</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-sub">Sitting with what's heavy without running to your phone, the fridge, or Netflix.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="page-letters__list-num">Letter IV</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-title">Alignment — one authentic choice at a time</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-sub">What an aligned life actually looks like. Hint: it's built in small moments, not grand exits.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="page-letters__list-num">Letter V</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-title">Alone, together</span>
          <span class="page-letters__list-sub">Why you can't do all of it alone — and your invitation to practice with us.</span>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <!-- ── § iii — After the letters ── -->
    <div class="page-letters__section">
      <p class="page-letters__marker">&sect; iii</p>
      <h2 class="page-letters__heading">What happens after letter five</h2>

      <p class="page-letters__body">
        You're invited to the <strong>Journal Club</strong> — Saturday mornings, online, free.
        25 minutes of guided meditation, journaling and honest connection.
        A weekly ritual to untangle the week and practice listening to your self, together.
      </p>
      <p class="page-letters__body">
        From there, everything is optional and nothing is pushed:
        weekly reflection prompts, gatherings in your city, the SEEKER cap, 1:1 guidance.
        You take what serves your journey and leave the rest.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ── § iv — Personal note ── -->
    <div class="page-letters__section">
      <p class="page-letters__marker">&sect; iv</p>
      <h2 class="page-letters__heading">Why I write them</h2>

      <p class="page-letters__body">
        I spent years succeeding at a life that wasn't mine — smiling on cue, collecting achievements that felt like sand.
        What changed wasn't a retreat or a guru. It was learning to sit down, get quiet, and actually listen.
        Hyper Real Love is the practice I wish someone had handed me at the start.
        These letters are that beginning.
      </p>
      <p class="page-letters__signature">— Daniel, Berlin</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Final CTA + form ── -->
    <div class="page-letters__section page-letters__final" id="letters-form">
      <h2 class="page-letters__heading page-letters__final-heading">Start with the first letter</h2>
      <p class="page-letters__body-em">Get to know your self better. Learn to listen.<br>Start living a life that is aligned with you — alone and in community.</p>

      <div class="page-letters__form">
        <script async data-uid="a433277e18" src="https://hyper-real-love-2.kit.com/a433277e18/index.js"></script>
      </div>

      <p class="page-letters__cta-note">Free. No spam. Unsubscribe anytime — no hard feelings.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.page-letters {
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding: 140px var(--space-6) var(--space-20);
  color: var(--color-yellow);
}

.page-letters__inner {
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* ── Hero ── */
.page-letters__hero {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-20);
}

.page-letters__eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-md);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  opacity: 0.7;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
}

.page-letters__title {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 56px);
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
}

.page-letters__title em { font-style: italic; }

.page-letters__subtitle {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  line-height: 1.6;
  opacity: 0.85;
  max-width: 520px;
  margin: 0 auto var(--space-10);
}

.page-letters__cta-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  color: var(--color-black);
  background: var(--color-yellow);
  padding: 14px 36px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: opacity var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
}

.page-letters__cta-btn:hover {
  opacity: 0.85;
  transform: scale(1.03);
}

.page-letters__cta-note {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  font-style: italic;
  opacity: 0.6;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-top: var(--space-4);
}

/* ── Sections ── */
.page-letters__section {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-20);
}

.page-letters__marker {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  font-style: italic;
  opacity: 0.5;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
}

.page-letters__heading {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 34px);
  line-height: 1.25;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
}

.page-letters__body {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-md);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.page-letters__body-em {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-top: var(--space-6);
}

/* ── Mirror list (recognition) ── */
.page-letters__mirror {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.page-letters__mirror li {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-md);
  line-height: 1.7;
  padding: var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
  position: relative;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 251, 41, 0.15);
}

.page-letters__mirror li::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--color-yellow);
  opacity: 0.6;
}

/* ── Letters list ── */
.page-letters__list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  counter-reset: letter;
}

.page-letters__list li {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-1);
  padding: var(--space-5) 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 251, 41, 0.15);
}

.page-letters__list-num {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  font-style: italic;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  opacity: 0.55;
}

.page-letters__list-title {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.page-letters__list-sub {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-md);
  font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.6;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

/* ── Signature ── */
.page-letters__signature {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  font-style: italic;
  margin-top: var(--space-6);
}

/* ── Final CTA ── */
.page-letters__final {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  scroll-margin-top: 120px;
}

.page-letters__final-heading { margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }

.page-letters__form {
  max-width: 480px;
  margin: var(--space-8) auto 0;
}

/* ── Mobile ── */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .page-letters { padding-top: 120px; }
  .page-letters__hero { margin-bottom: var(--space-16); }
  .page-letters__section { margin-bottom: var(--space-16); }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Letters",
